    <div class="py-2">
      <!-- <text class="text-lg">
        This is <b>Astrofy</b> a free and open-source template for your Personal Portfolio Website built with Astro and TailwindCSS.
        Create in minutes a website with Blog, CV, Project Section, Store and RSS Feed. I hope you find
        it useful!
      </text> -->
    </div>


    <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
      <div class="text-xl w-full font-bold">Open to:</div> 
        <li>AI Engineering and Backend Development</li>
        <li>Data Engineering and Machine Learning Engineering with AWS </li>
        <li>Machine Learning, Deep Learning and Generative AI Research </li>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
      <div class="text-xl w-full font-bold">Research Interests:</div> 
        <li>Computer Vision</li>
