      <li>Large Language Models/ Vision Language Models/ RAG </li>
    </div>


    <div class="mt-8">
      <a class="btn" href="https://linkedin.com/in/mizbaulhaquemaruf" target="_blank"> Let's connect!</a>
      <!-- <a href="https://github.com/manuelernestog/astrofy" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline ml-5">
